    XcconfigStack

    public static class XcconfigStack.Builder
extends Object
    Builder class for XcconfigStack objects. Layers and settings are taken by increasing order of priority (last one wins). $(inherited) tokens are replaced by (internal, generated, indirect) references to the previous layers.
